<li class="newsItem">
			<div class="nt-title">Rimrock Parent-Student Newsletters</div>
			<div class=""><p class="">Welcome back! As we return from spring break, we are embarking on a new journey of utilizing a virtual classroom environment for our students.</p></div>
			<a href="/news#rimrockparentstudentnewsletters" aria-label="Rimrock Parent-Student Newsletters news article">Read more...</a>
		</li>
<li class="newsItem">
